actor Customer
participant KIOSK

opt SIM Registration
KIOSK->Customer: Prompt customer to  enter address details

Customer->KIOSK: Enters address details  (Street, LGA, State)

KIOSK->Customer:    Prompt customer to  enter location of origin

Customer->KIOSK: Enters location details  (State, LGA)
end
opt SIM SWAP
space -3
Customer->KIOSK: Enter FQN
Customer->KIOSK: Enter Last Recharge
Customer->KIOSK: Enter Date of Activation
end

KIOSK->Customer: Prompt for fingerprint capture
Customer->KIOSK: Places finger on device
space -3
KIOSK->KIOSK: Captures finger print
space -3
KIOSK->Customer: Prompt to give digital consent

Customer->KIOSK: Confirms digital consent
KIOSK->KIOSK:   Display customer  data  before  final confirmation
space -3
Customer->KIOSK: Confirms data for final \n processing
KIOSK->KIOSK: Saves Data for payment
space -3
KIOSK->Customer: Displays Payment prompt \n.        for confirmation
